				<img src="images/logo1.jpg" width="130" height="130" title="Zachrome" alt="Zachrome" class="r-pic" />
				<p>R.Wilson &amp; Co (Platers) Ltd was established in 1947, Zachrome is a trading name from a Chrome Plating process developed for the automotive market. We moved to our present site in 1950 where we now have over 25,000 square ft of manufacturing &amp; office space &amp; modern facilities with overhead craneage for up to 3 tonne.</p>
				<p>We are specialist chromium platers and are pleased to advise from design through to finish with over 60 years experience at your disposal. If you are looking for chromium plating services then look no further than Zachrome.</p>
